            <p class="apn-nutr-product-meta"><strong>25 to 30g (1 scoop) within 45 minutes post-training</strong> for acute MPS. Also effective as a between-meal protein bridge when whole food is not available. Use between meals 2 and 3, or between meals 3 and 4, to add a 5th leucine-threshold trigger on high-demand days.</p>
