        <p class="apn-nutr-product-price">$34.99</p>
        <p class="apn-nutr-product-desc">Daily micronutrient foundation covering the gaps between whole food intake and what performance demands.</p>

        <div style="display:grid;gap:12px;margin-top:16px;">
          <div style="background:#F8F8F8;padding:14px 16px;border-radius:3px;">
            <p style="font-family:'Barlow',sans-serif;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:3px;color:#06A5C5;margin-bottom:6px;">The Mechanism</p>
            <p class="apn-nutr-product-meta">Training athletes have higher micronutrient turnover than sedentary individuals due to increased oxidative stress and sweating. A greens formula addresses the most common performance-limiting deficiencies: Vitamin K2 (bone metabolism and cardiovascular), B-complex vitamins (energy metabolism and neurotransmitter synthesis), and antioxidant botanicals that buffer the oxidative load of hard training. This is not a replacement for whole vegetables. It is an insurance layer on top of them.</p>
