            <p style="font-family:'Barlow',sans-serif;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:3px;color:#06A5C5;margin-bottom:6px;">Dose and Timing</p>
            <p class="apn-nutr-product-meta"><strong>1 serving daily, in the morning</strong> with 8 to 12oz of water or blended into your first meal. Morning timing ensures B-vitamins are available for energy metabolism throughout the day's training and cognitive demands.</p>
